research_municipality_step.notes: The Mayor, Kimberly Allphin, was elected on May 3, 2025, and installed on May 19, 2025. The Mayor Pro-Tem position is currently listed as 'to be determined' on the City of Plantersville website. The roles of Alderman and Board Secretary are based on information from the City of Plantersville website and the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory.
